same credit card must be presented upon check-in</strong></p>\r\n</li>\t\r\n </ul>\r\n </td>\r\n </tr>\r\n \r\n\r\n <tr>\r\n <td colspan=\"2\" style=\"padding-bottom:8px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#555;line-height:25px;display:block;text-decoration:underline\">Children &amp; Extra Beds</span></td>\r\n </tr>\r\n\r\n\r\n <tr>\r\n <td colspan=\"2\">\r\n <ul style=\"padding:0;margin:0\">\r\n <li style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:#555;line-height:20px;font-weight:400;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:justify;background:url(https://ci3.googleusercontent.com/meips/ADKq_NY-Mjqhaw0HQgzWnWDVbRdjutQcYnQDNYpMEJYILlpC4MGdnHg4ELIiUushamHzgnttDmWG44tEaZXK5btnQcuJsclu13ahxw=s0-d-e1-ft#https://my.innsight.com/assets/newemail/bullet.png) no-repeat;background-position:-2px 5px;display:inline-block;padding-left:15px\"><p>Children are always welcome. Those over 18 are considered adults. A crib can be requested for free for children between the ages of one and three.&nbsp; We do not offer cots or rollaway beds.</p>\r\n</li>\t\r\n\r\n </ul>\r\n\r\n </td>\r\n </tr>\r\n \r\n\r\n <tr>\r\n <td colspan=\"2\" style=\"padding-bottom:8px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#555;line-height:25px;display:block;text-decoration:underline\">Pets</span></td>\r\n </tr>\r\n\r\n\r\n <tr>\r\n <td colspan=\"2\">\r\n <ul style=\"padding:0;margin:0\">\r\n <li style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:#555;line-height:20px;font-weight:400;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:justify;background:url(https://ci3.googleusercontent.com/meips/ADKq_NY-Mjqhaw0HQgzWnWDVbRdjutQcYnQDNYpMEJYILlpC4MGdnHg4ELIiUushamHzgnttDmWG44tEaZXK5btnQcuJsclu13ahxw=s0-d-e1-ft#https://my.innsight.com/assets/newemail/bullet.png) no-repeat;background-position:-2px 5px;display:inline-block;padding-left:15px\"><p>Pets are not permitted to stay with us. Service dogs are welcome.</p>\r\n</li>\t\r\n\r\n </ul>\r\n\r\n </td>\r\n </tr>\r\n <tr>\r\n <td c