. All special requests are subject to availability upon check in. Special requests cannot be guaranteed and may require additional cost. All special requests are subject to availability upon check in.</li>\r\n\t<li style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:#555;line-height:20px;font-weight:400;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:justify;background:url(https://ci3.googleusercontent.com/meips/ADKq_NY-Mjqhaw0HQgzWnWDVbRdjutQcYnQDNYpMEJYILlpC4MGdnHg4ELIiUushamHzgnttDmWG44tEaZXK5btnQcuJsclu13ahxw=s0-d-e1-ft#https://my.innsight.com/assets/newemail/bullet.png) no-repeat;background-position:-2px 5px;display:inline-block;padding-left:15px\">Extra beds and baby cots are upon request and need to be confirmed by the INN. Supplements will not be calculated automatically in the total costs and have to be paid separately in the hotel.</li>\r\n\t<li style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:#555;line-height:20px;font-weight:400;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:left;background:url(https://ci3.googleusercontent.com/meips/ADKq_NY-Mjqhaw0HQgzWnWDVbRdjutQcYnQDNYpMEJYILlpC4MGdnHg4ELIiUushamHzgnttDmWG44tEaZXK5btnQcuJsclu13ahxw=s0-d-e1-ft#https://my.innsight.com/assets/newemail/bullet.png) no-repeat;background-position:-2px 5px;display:inline-block;padding-left:15px\">If you would like to cancel or modify your reservation please visit your My INNsight page or click on the appropriate reservation in the Upcoming Reservations list by clicking here: <a href=\"https://my.innsight.com/reservation-status/NzYxNjMw\" style=\"color:#555\" title=\"Cancel / Modify Reservation\" target=\"_blank\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?q=https://my.innsight.com/reservation-status/NzYxNjMw&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1717655976368000&amp;usg=AOvVaw2vZFzRjmS4xpiZKz6fbFXa\">https://my.innsight.com/<wbr>reservation-status/NzYxNjMw</a></li>\r\n\t<li style=\"font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:#555;line-height:20px;font-weight:400;margin-bottom:25px;text-align:justify;background:url(https://ci3.googleusercontent.com/meips/ADKq_NY-Mjqhaw0HQgzWnWDVbRdjutQcYnQDNYpMEJYILlpC4MGdnHg4ELIiUushamHzgnttDmWG44tEaZXK5btnQcuJsclu13ahxw=s0-d-e1-ft#https://my.innsight.com/assets/newemail/bullet.png) no-repeat;background-position:-2px 5px;display:inline-block;padding-left:15px\">Please contact the hotel directly or <a href=\"mailto:help@innsight.com\" title=\"Help\" target=\"_blank\">help@innsight.com</a> should you have any questions or issues with your reservation; in addition, you can leave a message at (408) 508-4667 and one of our agents will contact you.</li>\r\n</ul> </div>\r\n </td>\r\n </tr>\r\n\r\n <tr>\r\n <td colspan=\"2\" style=\"padding:10px;background-color:#056ac1\"><h2 style=\"text-align:center;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-size:20px;letter-spacing:0.5px;font-weight:500;margin:0\"><a href=\"https://www.heritagehotelnyc.com/New-York-City-attractions\" title=\"New York City City Guide\" style=\"color:#fff;text-decoration:none;display:block\" target=\"_blank\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.heritagehotelnyc.com/New-York-City-attractions&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1717655976368000&amp;usg=AOvVaw0XCAfzuvNd4hC20Y-bh-Pi\">Click Here For Our New York City City Guide</a></h2></td>\r\n </tr>\r\n\r\n <tr>\r\n <td colspan=\"2\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n </tr>\r\n\r\n </tbody></table>\r\n </td>\r\n </tr>\r\n\r\n </tbody></table>\r\n </td>\r\n\r\n <td width=\"25\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n\r\n </tr>\r\n\r\n </tbody></table>\r\n\r\n </td>\t\r\n\r\n <td width=\"35\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n\r\n </tr>\r\n\r\n \r\n <tr>\r\n <td colspan=\"3\" align=\"center\" style=\"padding:5px 0\">\r\n <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/heritagehotelnewyorkcity\" style=\"display:inline-block\" target=\"_blank\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.facebook.com/heritagehotelnewyorkcity&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1717655976368000&amp;usg=AOvVaw0uCQ-cM91w9RhGCY9yJd2-\"><img src=\"https://ci3.googleusercontent.com/meips/ADKq_Nan37Gi